          "contractorTier": "INTERMEDIATE",
          "description": "**Freelance Full-Stack Developer / Integration Engineer**\n\nWe are looking for a freelance developer to help finalize and productionize several internal apps and workflows built in Replit.\n\nThe apps are already partially built and functional, but now require:\n\n* API integrations\n* workflow refinement\n* bug fixing\n* UI/UX polishing\n* deployment readiness\n* overall technical review and cleanup\n\nKey integrations include:\n\n* Email systems\n* WhatsApp messaging\n* Stripe payments\n* Guesty PMS integration\n\nThe ideal candidate should be comfortable working with rapidly developed MVP-style applications and improving them into stable, production-ready tools.\n\nRequirements:\n\n* Strong full-stack development experience\n* Experience with APIs and third-party integrations\n* Comfortable working inside Replit environments\n* Experience with Stripe and messaging integrations\n* Ability to troubleshoot, optimize, and improve existing codebases\n* Good eye for usability and product polish\n\nBonus if you have experience with:\n\n* Hospitality tech\n* Property management systems (especially Guesty)\n* Automation workflows\n* AI-assisted development environments\n\nThis is initially a freelance/project-based role, but could evolve into an ongoing technical partnership for the right person.",
